### Health Check
### Returns version and timestamp - always 200 if server is running
### No authentication required

GET {{host}}/health

### Expected Response:
### {
###   "version": "1.0.0",
###   "timestamp": "2026-03-20T00:00:00.000Z"
### }


### Readiness Check
### Checks Redis and Azure deployment connectivity
### Returns 503 if dependencies are unavailable
### No authentication required

GET {{host}}/ready

### Expected Response (when ready):
### {
###   "status": "ready",
###   "checks": {
###     "redis": true,
###     "deployments": true
###   },
###   "timestamp": "2026-03-20T00:00:00.000Z"
### }

### Expected Response (when not ready - 503):
### {
###   "status": "not_ready",
###   "checks": {
###     "redis": false,
###     "deployments": true
###   },
###   "timestamp": "2026-03-20T00:00:00.000Z"
### }
